episodes.title: “THUSA nas BUAILTICHE a bhith ann an CULT” - Saor No Daor: Most Likely To Airgead Edition | BBC ALBA
episodes.description:
Christy O’Hanlon & Zachariah Ronan play a game of Most Likely To, and tell us who will be richer in the future. Watch Saor no Daor to see them flex their thrifty skills 💸👯

Tha Christy & Zach a’ cluich geama de Most Likely To, agus a’ cabadaich mu na spending habits aca. Faic Saor No Daor a-nis air YouTube & iPlayer.💰😍
